    <id>tag:www.unboxedconsulting.com,2015-12-09:donald-trump-block-petition-hits-270-000-signatures-and-rising</id>
    <title>Donald Trump block petition hits 400,000 signatures and rising</title>
    <summary type="html">A [petition to block the entry of Donald Trump](https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/114003) to the UK has risen to a total of 400,000 signatures from members of the public on the government Petitions site, and rising every minute.&lt;br/&gt;

Built as a partnership between Unboxed and GDS (Government Digital Service), Petitions enables members of the public to create or sign petitions that ask for a change to the law or to government policy.&lt;br/&gt;

The Donald Trump block petition has passed the 100,000-signature threshold in less than 24 hours. Petitions that receive 10,000 signatures get a response from the government, and those that receive 100,000 signatures are considered for debate in Parliament.&lt;br/&gt;

The Government &lt;b&gt;will&lt;/b&gt; respond to this petition and Parliament &lt;b&gt;will&lt;/b&gt; consider it for debate.&lt;br/&gt;

Our [Petition Map](https://petitionmap.unboxedconsulting.com) shows a visual heat map of which individual areas are signing this petition from across the UK.&lt;br/&gt;

Coverage of the story has featured in major UK publications:&lt;br/&gt;

&lt;blockquote class=&quot;twitter-tweet tw-align-center&quot;&gt;&lt;p lang=&quot;en&quot; dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;Petition calling for Republican presidential candidate Donald Trump to be barred from entering UK passes 100,000 &lt;a href=&quot;https://t.co/yOtNyRIMBv&quot;&gt;https://t.co/yOtNyRIMBv&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&amp;mdash; BBC Breaking News (@BBCBreaking) &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/BBCBreaking/status/674562411165294592&quot;&gt;December 9, 2015&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt; &lt;script async src=&quot;//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js&quot; charset=&quot;utf-8&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;blockquote class=&quot;twitter-tweet tw-align-center&quot;&gt;&lt;p lang=&quot;en&quot; dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;Ban on Trump entering Britain to be debated in Parliament after 100,000 sign petition &lt;a href=&quot;https://t.co/BzwNQA6xa5&quot;&gt;https://t.co/BzwNQA6xa5&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;https://t.co/tZ72VsVmeC&quot;&gt;pic.twitter.com/tZ72VsVmeC&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&amp;mdash; Daily Mail U.K. (@DailyMailUK) &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/DailyMailUK/status/674563917612498944&quot;&gt;December 9, 2015&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt; &lt;script async src=&quot;//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js&quot; charset=&quot;utf-8&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

