    <id>tag:www.unboxedconsulting.com,2015-07-14:masterclass-move-the-needle-on-your-website-kpis-in-3-hours</id>
    <title>Masterclass: Deliver 50% growth with Lean UX</title>
    <summary type="html">&lt;h2 class=&quot;super_sub_heading&quot;&gt;Find up to 50% more revenue from your website or 50% more conversion from your digital service during this 3-hour masterclass&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;br/&gt;
Join Unboxed on Wednesday 12th August for a hands on 3-hour session where you will  try out the powerful analytics-led design techniques Unboxed used to help:&lt;br/&gt;
• Online travel company, [Contiki Holidays](https://www.unboxedconsulting.com/project-stories/contiki-holidays), increase bookings by &lt;b&gt;47%&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
• Pioneering NHS digital sexual health service, [SH:24](https://www.unboxedconsulting.com/project-stories/sh24), increase the number of people completing the order process to &lt;b&gt;95%&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;

&lt;b&gt;Date:&lt;/b&gt; Wednesday 12th August&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;b&gt;Time :&lt;/b&gt; 9.30am – 12.30pm (coffee and warm up fun from 9.00am)&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;b&gt;Location:&lt;/b&gt; Adam House, 7-10 Adam Street, London, WC2N 6AA&lt;br/&gt;

&lt;p align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.eventbrite.co.uk/e/masterclass-deliver-50-growth-with-lean-ux-tickets-17761740845?ref=ebtn&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://www.eventbrite.co.uk/custombutton?eid=17761740845&quot; alt=&quot;Eventbrite - Masterclass: Deliver 50% growth with Lean UX&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt; 

&lt;font size=&quot;4&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;The experts:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/font&gt;

&lt;p align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://bit.ly/1TxhoXO&quot; alt=&quot;The experts&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt; 

&lt;font size=&quot;4&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;[Richard Stobart](https://www.unboxedconsulting.com/people/richard-stobart) – CEO at Unboxed Consulting&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/font&gt;
Agile Coach of the Year 2014, Richard is one of the UK’s leading experts in the process of digital product design for valuable, commercial features.&lt;br/&gt;

&lt;font size=&quot;4&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;[Dominic Mason](https://www.unboxedconsulting.com/people/dominic-mason) – Client Partner at Unboxed Consulting&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/font&gt; 
Dom works with dozens of companies each year to design projects that deliver huge value, quickly. He speaks business, technical, Agile and project.&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;

&lt;h2 class=&quot;super_sub_heading&quot;&gt;The event in detail&lt;/h2&gt;
This masterclass is best for optimising strategic products with a long lifespan, for example:&lt;br/&gt;
• Website and digital services with at least a two-year lifecycle&lt;br/&gt;
• eCommerce websites&lt;br/&gt;
• Public sector digital services&lt;br/&gt;
• Membership sites&lt;br/&gt;
• Group intranets&lt;br/&gt;

&lt;h2 class=&quot;super_sub_heading&quot;&gt;Who should attend?&lt;/h2&gt;
• Those tasked with significantly increasing the revenue, conversion or performance of a website or digital service&lt;br/&gt;
• People who have inherited a website or digital service and need fresh ways to increase its performance&lt;br/&gt;
• ..or who have worked &lt;i&gt;&#39;in the trenches&#39;&lt;/i&gt; on same website or digital service for a long time&lt;br/&gt;


&lt;h2 class=&quot;super_sub_heading&quot;&gt;Expect to learn how to:&lt;/h2&gt;
• Learn a methodology for creating new &lt;i&gt;‘greenfield’&lt;/i&gt; Key Performance Indicator improvements&lt;br/&gt;
• Step up a level to the strategic product view – create more value&lt;br/&gt;
• Go beyond organic: Find new and unexpected sources of uplift in this metric&lt;br/&gt;
• Understand what drives your metrics and how to use &lt;i&gt;‘smart KPI branching’&lt;/i&gt; to discover how users really behave&lt;br/&gt;
• Get more out of a mature product which is in diminishing returns&lt;br/&gt;
• Make a concrete plan for delivering the commercial return the business demands from the website or digital service&lt;br/&gt;

