    <id>tag:www.unboxedconsulting.com,2015-02-23:event-unstick-your-digital-products</id>
    <title>Event: Unstick your digital products: Rapidly progress a complex product or portfolio of stalled products</title>
    <summary type="html">&lt;b&gt;Date:&lt;/b&gt; Wednesday 25th March&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;b&gt;Time:&lt;/b&gt; 9.00am – 12.30pm (coffee and warm up fun from 8.30am!)&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;b&gt;Location:&lt;/b&gt; Skills Matter, 116-120 Goswell Road, London, EC1V 7DP
&lt;br/&gt;

Join us on 25th March for an energetic three-hour session where you’ll learn a series of techniques to:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
• Accelerate a product that’s buried under features&lt;br/&gt;
• Get a large product portfolio moving again&lt;br/&gt;
• Move faster to catch up with a competitor&lt;br/&gt;
• Get traction in a non-Agile organisation&lt;br/&gt;
• Focus limited resources on what will create most value&lt;br/&gt;

Our speakers include:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;h2 class=&quot;super_sub_heading&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;i&gt;“Trust me, I’m a product manager”&lt;/i&gt;: case study from publishing&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;i&gt;Dave Evans - Product Manager (E-commerce) at Nature Publishing Group&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;

![Event0](http://i1291.photobucket.com/albums/b548/grammccram/Screen%20Shot%202015-03-12%20at%2014.29.18_zpsrf53xobd.png)

The foundation of speed is trust. Dave will talk through how to establish trust rapidly with stakeholders, how to demonstrate value and be seen as the expert.&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;

&lt;h2 class=&quot;super_sub_heading&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;How designing a new experience in the NHS helped to unblock and unleash new potential&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;i&gt;Glyn Parry – Programme Manager at SH:24 (NHS collaboration)&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;

Glyn Parry explains why an iterative and agile approach has been used to turn STI testing on its head - challenging deep seated practices and prejudices in the NHS and local authorities.&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;

&lt;h2 class=&quot;super_sub_heading&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Techniques for overcoming the top digital product blockers&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;i&gt;Richard Stobart – CEO, Unboxed Consulting, Agile Coach of the Year 2014&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;

![Event2](http://i1291.photobucket.com/albums/b548/grammccram/Screen%20Shot%202015-03-03%20at%2016.22.05_zps53cqwbt3.png)

Exactly why digital products get stuck and techniques to speed them up again.&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;

