• Thomas Whicher - Founder,  DrDoctor&lt;br/&gt;
• Ian Drysdale - CTO, GoodGym&lt;br/&gt;

The format is simple - three presentations from within the group, followed by a single conversation around the table. The aim is to learn from each other and find better ways to use digital technology already available to us.&lt;br/&gt;</summary>
