    <title>Contiki launches a video competition site in time for Movember</title>
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;Contiki, the global tours operator for 18-35 year olds has once again teamed up with Unboxed Consulting to launch two new sites: a video competition site and &lt;a href=&quot;http://za.contiki.com/contikicares/&quot;&gt;Contiki Cares&lt;/a&gt;. The competition site engages travellers and encourages them to share activities though videos, photos and stories. Fellow travellers then choose and vote for the best entry. Fittingly &lt;a href=&quot;http://contiki.co.uk/contests/movember-grow-mo-or-faux-mo&quot;&gt;Movember&lt;/a&gt; is the first competition and includes both real and faux mo&amp;nbsp;entries (for the ladies)&amp;nbsp;with the closing date of 10 December.&lt;/p&gt;
