&lt;p&gt;This follows on from the launch of &lt;a href=&quot;http://za.contiki.com/contikicares/&quot;&gt;Contiki Cares&lt;/a&gt; which showcases Contiki&amp;#39;s socially responsible projects. It features their partnership with the &lt;a href=&quot;http://za.contiki.com/contikicares/mar-leaders&quot;&gt;Mesoamerican Reef (MAR) Leadership Program&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;which supports young, local environmentalists as well as&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;http://za.contiki.com/contikicares/oceana&quot;&gt;Oceana&lt;/a&gt;, an organisation dedicated to protecting and restoring oceans of the world.&amp;nbsp;Unboxed Consulting created a microsite that included integration with&amp;nbsp;YouTube,&amp;nbsp;Facebook, Twitter, Google+ and other social media platforms to create a customised social media feed.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Both solutions were created to give Contiki&amp;rsquo;s editors maximum flexibility through their content management system, providing them with the ability to fully customise blocks of HTML and CSS styled content.&lt;/p&gt;
